item.title: Help urgent
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

[quote=“ProjectPvpTehe, post:3, topic:437328”]spawn = 1294 3086 3492 0 0 0 0 0 Donator points shop

that is my error how i fix?[/quote]

He told you. You use tabs instead of spaces.

spawn = 1294	3086	3492	0	0	0	0	0	Donator points shop

When you’re inputting it, instead of doing this:

spawn = 1294(space)3086(space)3492(space)0(space)0(space)0(space)0(space)0(space)Donator points shop

You do this:

spawn(space)=(space)1294(tab)3086(tab)3492(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)Donator points shop
